The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
City: paris, colone, edinburgh
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, subway, train
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the fan of trance and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the fan of trance and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the fan of punk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk     | classical |
| City   | paris | colone | edinburgh   |
| Transport     | train   | subway   | bike      |

