.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, writer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, september
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Birthday   | april     | january      | september    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

