.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, january, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's birthday is in august##2
4. the fan of reggae is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Birthday         | january   | february | august |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

